&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;322&quot; data-start=&quot;169&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;322&quot; data-start=&quot;171&quot;&gt;In &lt;strong data-end=&quot;182&quot; data-start=&quot;174&quot;&gt;2025&lt;/strong&gt;, the &lt;strong data-end=&quot;212&quot; data-start=&quot;188&quot;&gt;global unicorn count&lt;/strong&gt; reached a &lt;strong data-end=&quot;248&quot; data-start=&quot;223&quot;&gt;record 1,523 startups&lt;/strong&gt;, valued at over &lt;strong data-end=&quot;284&quot; data-start=&quot;265&quot;&gt;$1 billion each&lt;/strong&gt;, totaling &lt;strong data-end=&quot;312&quot; data-start=&quot;295&quot;&gt;$5.6 trillion&lt;/strong&gt; in value.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;446&quot; data-start=&quot;323&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;446&quot; data-start=&quot;325&quot;&gt;A &lt;strong data-end=&quot;338&quot; data-start=&quot;327&quot;&gt;unicorn&lt;/strong&gt; is a &lt;strong data-end=&quot;370&quot; data-start=&quot;344&quot;&gt;privately held startup&lt;/strong&gt; with a &lt;strong data-end=&quot;407&quot; data-start=&quot;378&quot;&gt;valuation over $1 billion&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;mdash;term coined by &lt;strong data-end=&quot;445&quot; data-start=&quot;423&quot;&gt;Aileen Lee in 2013&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
