	&lt;ul data-end=&quot;1001&quot; data-start=&quot;882&quot;&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;1001&quot; data-start=&quot;882&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;1001&quot; data-start=&quot;884&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;897&quot; data-start=&quot;884&quot;&gt;Bengaluru&lt;/strong&gt; is India&amp;rsquo;s top unicorn hub (&lt;strong data-end=&quot;946&quot; data-start=&quot;926&quot;&gt;rank #7 globally&lt;/strong&gt;), followed by &lt;strong data-end=&quot;977&quot; data-start=&quot;961&quot;&gt;Mumbai (#22)&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong data-end=&quot;1000&quot; data-start=&quot;982&quot;&gt;Gurugram (#27)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
